data.title: Cemil Cahit Toydemir
data.meta_description: Cemil Cahit Toydemir was an officer of the Ottoman Army and a general of the Turkish Army of Circassian origin. He served in Caucasus front in WWI, after Armistice of Mudros he joined Turkish National Movement and attended Sivas Congress.
